g points to encourage reflection and a wide range of examples to illustrate practice, Teach Now! The Essentials of Teaching provides expert guidance as you start your exciting and rewarding career as an outstanding teacher"--cProvided by publisher.  a41 0aTeaching. 0aTeachersxTraining of. 0aTeach now!  aLB 1025.3 B365 2015c1hUAED-Bi0162035221850  aLB 1025.3 B365 2015wLCc1i0162035221850d2/23/2016e1/10/2016lFLOOR_2mUAEDUCn6p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu1/21/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/nb2004301591bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/85102989